result.notes: This sub datalayer comprises marine and associated intertidal sites, findspots and palaeoenvironmental deposits and features located within the search area that date from the prehistoric period (deemed for the purposes of this study as dating from between 500,000 years BP up to the Roman period AD 43). One of a series of 4 Maritime Archaeology sub datalayers.
